| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0322 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4c89cd64-f03f-5de0-8e3e-19e1c75dfaee"
